      <description>xc - Markdown defined task runner.   Define project tasks within the README.md file, similar to npm scripts or a Makefile, but more human readable.
The intent is to be a convenient task runner for any type of project, and if the runner isn&amp;rsquo;t installed the syntax is human readable.
Installation Go: go install github.com/joe-davidson1802/xc/cmd/xc@latest Brew: brew tap joe-davidson1802/xc brew install xc (Optional) Install tab completion for bash: xc -complete When keys xc&amp;lt;Tab&amp;gt; are pressed, completion should be triggered:</description>
